shortDescription:
EWAYBY is committed to providing people with a more soulful life. Its 3-Piece Reversible Floral Pattern Quilt Sets can be used to add texture to your bedroom decor. The set includes 1 quilt and 2 pillow shams, which give a conpleted look of the decorative design. The Floral Patchwork Patterns bring people positive emotions. Uniform and fine quilting lines to ensure that it can be washed multiple times without running cotton or deformed, can be directly machine washed, it is very easy to care. 

Key Feature:
  • [High Quality Material] Woven of 100% microfiber cover and filling. Microfiber quilts can be soften after washing, the material features NO fade, NO shrink, NO pilling and stains resistant than cotton which will last for all year round.
  • [Unique Design] Floral Patchwork Patterns is a unique print for an all-American look. Using a new generation of active printing and dyeing technology ensurs that it is environmental friendly and health
  • [Multi-Purpose] Used for decoration or warmth. Coverlets work well in cold climates or seasons as an additional layer atop your comforter or duvet, but they can also be used as your main bedding option in warm climates or seasons. Adding a coverlet is an easy way to change your bedding, just remove, fold, or display however you desire.
  • [Easy to Clean] Machine wash cold and dry quickly, Since they are lightweight, they are easier to wash than a thick quilt or fluffy comforter.

Available Size:
  • Queen: Quilt (90 *98 Inch)  Matched Pillowcases (20 *27 Inch)
  • King: Quilt (96*108 Inch)   Matched Pillowcases (20 *36 Inch)

Product Specification:
  • Product Name: EWAYBY 3-Piece Reversible Floral Pattern Quilt 
  • Color: Retro Red, Black Orange, Calaite, Coffee, Grey, Mint Green, Purple, Rose Red, Sky Blue
  • Design: Floral Pattern Decor Friendly Colors
  • Material: 100% microfiber

Package Include:
  • 1X Quilt + 2 X Matched Pillowcases
